        "jsCode": "// DFW Time Check - America/Chicago timezone\nconst now = new Date();\nconst dfwTime = new Date(now.toLocaleString('en-US', { timeZone: 'America/Chicago' }));\nconst hour = dfwTime.getHours();\n// Operating hours: 7am to 11pm (7 to 22)\nconst isWithinHours = hour >= 7 && hour < 23;\n\n// Generate BOTH products every execution\nreturn [\n  { json: { isWithinHours, currentHour: hour, product: 'uad' } },\n  { json: { isWithinHours, currentHour: hour, product: 'missparty' } }\n];"
